### Variables (VS Code REST Client / similar)
@base = http://localhost:8000
@token = paste_jwt_here

### Health
GET {{base}}/health

### Register
POST {{base}}/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "learner@example.com",
  "password": "securepass123",
  "full_name": "Ada Learner"
}

### Login
POST {{base}}/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "learner@example.com",
  "password": "securepass123"
}

### Generate path (explicit level)
POST {{base}}/generate-path
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "skills": ["Python", "Machine Learning"],
  "goal": "Data Scientist",
  "experience_level": "Beginner",
  "hours_per_day": 1.5,
  "regenerate_smarter": false,
  "use_cache": true
}

### Regenerate smarter (skip cache, richer LLM)
POST {{base}}/generate-path
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "skills": ["Python", "Docker"],
  "goal": "DevOps Engineer",
  "experience_level": "Intermediate",
  "hours_per_day": 2,
  "regenerate_smarter": true,
  "use_cache": false
}

### Step feedback
POST {{base}}/feedback
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "step_index": 0,
  "phase_name": "Linux & Scripting",
  "status": "not_understood",
  "generation_id": "paste_generation_objectid"
}

### List feedback
GET {{base}}/feedback
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Generate path (infer level)
POST {{base}}/generate-path
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "skills": ["Python", "Docker", "Kubernetes"],
  "goal": "DevOps Engineer",
  "experience_level": null,
  "hours_per_day": 2
}

### History
GET {{base}}/history
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
